parameters:
During the break in physical education class, I
will be in charge of disciplining the student who
engaged in misconduct. I will patrol around the
school vicinity near dismissal time.

This is already a routine that has been repeated
for over ten years.

Usually, I give warnings to students who take
detours and enforce regulations on inappropriate
relationships between students of the opposite
sex.

Sometimes, there are students who engage in
misconduct that cannot be overlooked, although
usually it is enough to just give warnings to the
students who are excited during dismissal time.
\n<Teacher>What are you all doing at this time?

\n<Teacher>You guys commute by train, right? The station is
on the opposite side.
\n<Teacher>Where on earth were you planning to go?

\n<Female Student B>Ugh... Seriously, what's the deal? And seriously,
why are you prying into what we do after school?
It's none of your business~
\n<Female Student C>No way! It's sexual harassment, sexual harassment!
\n<Female Student A>By the way, what does セクハラ stand for?

\n<Female Student C>Sexual harassment... sexual harassment... sex
paradise!

\n<Female Student B>Pa huh? Hahaha, if that's the case, it'll turn
into a sex paradise! Hahaha

\n<Female Student A>It's fine, let's make it go viral with Sex-Para!
LOL
\n<Teacher>Stop saying stupid things and go home already.

\n<Female Student A>Huh? I don't want to. We're going to karaoke and
singing all night.
\n<Female Student B>Hey! Idiot! You can't say that!
\n<Female Student C>Oh no... Let's run away!

The guidance of students who have completely
underestimated the world requires time, patience,
and physical stamina.

After catching the delinquent students that day, I
gave them a thorough scolding.

In the end, due to contacting the parents and
handling the aftermath, it turned out that they
had to go home by the last train.
